  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to lxqt-globalkeys</title>

    <para>
      The <application>lxqt-globalkeys</application> package contains a daemon
      used to register global keyboard shortcuts and a key shortcut GUI editor.
    </para>

    &lfs82_checked;

